01:20:27.777 --> 01:20:30.725
Please, could I ask you,
just give us one more half hour.

01:20:30.725 --> 01:20:31.931
She's been working
all day on this dessert.

01:20:31.931 --> 01:20:32.746
I have.

01:20:32.746 --> 01:20:35.267
You won't be sorry.
One half hour more, okay?

01:20:35.267 --> 01:20:36.405
Please.

01:20:36.682 --> 01:20:38.661
- Okay, fine.
- All right. Great!

01:20:38.661 --> 01:20:43.456
Okay. Let's move into the living room.
It is such a pleasure to know you two.

01:20:43.597 --> 01:20:45.467
- Shh! Shh! Shh! Shh!
- What?

01:20:45.467 --> 01:20:48.143
- Shh. I heard him at the phone.
- So?

01:20:49.648 --> 01:20:52.059
He said that he loved her
and he wanted to marry her.

01:20:52.059 --> 01:20:53.976
I even know her name.
Maria!

01:20:54.209 --> 01:20:57.492
"Maria, I love you. Maria, I wanna
marry you." Just like the song.

01:20:57.492 --> 01:20:59.250
I was waitin' for him
to start singin' and dancin'.

01:20:59.250 --> 01:21:00.722
Oh, my God.

01:21:00.722 --> 01:21:03.482
This guy has got balls
this big.

01:21:03.482 --> 01:21:05.753
She calls right here,
right under her nose.

01:21:05.753 --> 01:21:09.027
Some psychic she is. Her own husband
is in love with a woman named Maria,

01:21:09.027 --> 01:21:11.735
- and she doesn't even know it!
- I feel so sorry for her.

01:21:12.196 --> 01:21:14.250
They are not psychic,
they're psychotic.

01:21:14.250 --> 01:21:16.383
What kind of a woman makes
an armadillo meat loaf

01:21:16.383 --> 01:21:18.113
and God knows
what was in those eggs.

01:21:18.236 --> 01:21:19.591
- Pam.
- What?

01:21:19.715 --> 01:21:22.964
I wouldn't be surprised if this guy killed
his first wife. We gotta get outta here.

01:21:22.964 --> 01:21:25.473
- Let's go.
- No! No, no, no, we...

01:21:25.473 --> 01:21:26.299
Be right there!

01:21:26.299 --> 01:21:27.487
Oh, knowing these two,

01:21:27.487 --> 01:21:28.535
they will bring the dessert
to our house.

01:21:28.535 --> 01:21:30.156
Okay, listen, we'll just
sit down and eat fast.

01:21:30.156 --> 01:21:31.683
Fast, fast! Eat fast! Eat fast!

01:21:31.684 --> 01:21:34.407
- All we got's ice cream sandwiches.
- We'll tell 'em it's homemade.

01:21:35.813 --> 01:21:38.776
- We need somethin' else.
- Reddi-Wip.

01:21:38.788 --> 01:21:42.365
Very good. It was a good cover
with the psychic thing.

01:21:42.583 --> 01:21:44.139
- You really think so?
- Yeah.

01:21:44.660 --> 01:21:46.820
Thank you.
How'd you get all wet?

01:21:46.820 --> 01:21:47.838
I snuck over to their house.

01:21:47.838 --> 01:21:49.963
I snuck over to their house
looking for Bill.

01:21:50.189 --> 01:21:51.720
- Yeah?
- And the sprinklers went off.

01:21:51.720 --> 01:21:53.999
- Oh, God. Did you find 'im?
- No, he wasn't there.

01:21:53.999 --> 01:21:55.386
- He wasn't there?
- No.

01:21:55.890 --> 01:21:57.003
Give me that.

01:21:58.137 --> 01:22:00.545
I wouldn't worry about this too much.
We're not gonna be invited over for dinner.

01:22:00.545 --> 01:22:01.529
They already think we're nuts.

01:22:01.529 --> 01:22:04.054
They don't think we're nuts.
We're a perfectly normal couple. Go.

01:22:04.313 --> 01:22:07.201
"I scream, you scream.
We all scream for ice cream."

01:22:07.535 --> 01:22:08.975
- Great.
- Oh, thank you.

01:22:08.975 --> 01:22:10.696
You're really gonna like this.
It's a specialty.

01:22:10.696 --> 01:22:11.451
Oh, honey.

01:22:11.473 --> 01:22:12.495
Doesn't this look great?

01:22:12.495 --> 01:22:14.519
Oh, yeah, looks real good.
Looks real good.

01:22:14.519 --> 01:22:16.354
Oh, mmm, this is wonderful.

01:22:16.354 --> 01:22:18.211
You're gonna have
to give me the recipe, okay?

01:22:18.255 --> 01:22:20.109
- I will.
- Okay.

01:22:20.248 --> 01:22:22.234
Oh, it's terrific.

01:22:28.533 --> 01:22:30.450
- Mmm.
- Mmm!

01:22:34.539 --> 01:22:37.511
Oh, God.
Headache, honey?

01:22:37.967 --> 01:22:39.435
Honey, honey.

01:22:39.795 --> 01:22:41.072
I think we'd better...

01:22:41.072 --> 01:22:42.466
I think we're gonna go home.

01:22:42.466 --> 01:22:43.814
- Yes, I think it's time for us to go.
- Yeah.

01:22:44.330 --> 01:22:46.164
- No! No, no, no!
- No, no, no.

01:22:46.164 --> 01:22:48.083
No, no, really,
we have to go.

01:22:48.397 --> 01:22:51.472
No, really, we... I have
an early tee time tomorrow morning.

01:22:51.799 --> 01:22:54.349
Thanks very much
for a very interesting evening.

01:22:54.349 --> 01:22:56.787
If-if... If you
could just... If you could just...

01:22:56.787 --> 01:22:59.507
Oh, the hell with this.
I'm goin' out there to find Bill.

01:22:59.839 --> 01:23:02.260
Well, get your badge.
They'll never believe you're a cop.

01:23:07.323 --> 01:23:09.537
- Oh, my God.
- Did you call the police?

01:23:09.537 --> 01:23:11.748
- No.
- Lu, you've gotta call the police.

01:23:11.748 --> 01:23:14.420
If I tell the police,
they'll take me back to testify.

01:23:14.664 --> 01:23:15.924
I have to leave.

01:23:15.924 --> 01:23:17.537
What about him?
What are you gonna do with him?

01:23:20.235 --> 01:23:21.895
- I'll have to kill 'im.
- Hmm?

01:23:23.263 --> 01:23:24.635
Brian, talk to her.

01:23:26.290 --> 01:23:29.190
- Shut up.
- Wait. Wait. Lu, wait a minute, now.

01:23:29.190 --> 01:23:30.232
What do you mean,
you're just gonna kill 'im?

01:23:30.232 --> 01:23:31.768
That's it?
You kill 'im and that's it?

01:23:31.981 --> 01:23:33.631
He came here to kill me.

01:23:34.967 --> 01:23:39.045
Shut up! Look, if he lives,
he'll tell them that you helped me.

01:23:39.045 --> 01:23:40.780
Then they're comin' after you.

01:23:41.087 --> 01:23:42.517
Shut up!

01:23:46.158 --> 01:23:48.383
Get up. Get up.
Come on.

01:23:57.160 --> 01:23:59.095
He's probably
havin' a beer somewhere.

01:24:11.835 --> 01:24:12.847
Shit.

01:26:00.014 --> 01:26:02.455
Try anything,
I'll shoot you. Get out.

01:26:02.455 --> 01:26:04.100
Come on, get up.

01:26:09.351 --> 01:26:10.824
I don't see them.

01:26:12.514 --> 01:26:15.494
Goddamn it.
Must have turned off.

01:26:16.220 --> 01:26:18.943
Come on, come on!
So how much was I worth, huh?

01:26:18.943 --> 01:26:21.645
25? 30,000?
Huh?

01:26:21.756 --> 01:26:23.152
Keep going.

01:26:23.512 --> 01:26:26.850
You shouldn't have come after me.
You just shouldn't have come.

01:26:26.850 --> 01:26:29.126
I wasn't gonna testify.

01:26:29.387 --> 01:26:32.914
Don't stop! You don't do
anything unless I tell you.

01:26:33.721 --> 01:26:36.009
Maybe you're the guy
that killed Michael. Huh?

01:26:36.009 --> 01:26:38.401
Are you?
Did you kill Michael?

01:26:38.401 --> 01:26:41.078
I bet you are,
you son of a bitch!

01:26:41.078 --> 01:26:43.909
I just bet you are.
You killed Michael, didn't you?

01:26:44.015 --> 01:26:46.034
Now I'm gonna kill you.
Get down!

01:26:49.624 --> 01:26:53.302
If you believe in God, you better
pray for forgiveness now.

01:26:53.302 --> 01:26:55.417
Because you got no time left.

01:27:34.834 --> 01:27:36.011
Watch out!

01:27:41.346 --> 01:27:42.616
Go get Bill!

01:27:52.134 --> 01:27:53.724
Hang on, Bill!

01:28:20.780 --> 01:28:21.761
Okay!

01:28:22.288 --> 01:28:23.293
Okay.

01:28:25.009 --> 01:28:25.985
- You all right?
- Yeah.

01:28:25.985 --> 01:28:27.200
- Are you okay?
- Yeah.

01:28:40.841 --> 01:28:42.632
Get away
from the dock!

01:28:46.242 --> 01:28:48.938
I'll get it!
I'm gonna get the car!

01:28:52.949 --> 01:28:54.086
- She okay?
- Yeah.

01:28:54.086 --> 01:28:55.198
How about you?

01:28:55.198 --> 01:28:57.439
- I'm fine. Where's Bill?
- Up there.

01:29:27.557 --> 01:29:30.061
Okay! I got 'er!

01:29:41.032 --> 01:29:42.448
Oo-ha!

01:29:43.325 --> 01:29:46.513
Whoo-hoo-hoo!
Whoo!

01:30:04.504 --> 01:30:07.467
<i>This is the final boarding call
for Flight 610...</i>

01:30:20.428 --> 01:30:20.800
Yep.

01:30:20.800 --> 01:30:22.853
They found her on
one of those islands near Seattle.

01:30:22.853 --> 01:30:25.072
Staying with some family
named O'Hara.

01:30:25.072 --> 01:30:27.820
- She's agreed to testify, am I right?
- I don't know yet.

01:30:27.820 --> 01:30:29.669
<i>We just got the call
from Seattle.</i>

01:30:29.669 --> 01:30:32.691
Don't worry about it. I'm catching
a plane, I'm bringin' her back.

01:30:32.691 --> 01:30:34.480
Look, I need to know
where she is right now.

01:30:34.480 --> 01:30:37.056
Do you follow me?
That woman...

01:30:39.442 --> 01:30:41.855
That woman...
will not testify.

01:30:41.855 --> 01:30:45.958
Yeah. I'll call
when I get there. Hey!

01:30:50.586 --> 01:30:51.908
Hello, Tony?

01:30:52.238 --> 01:30:56.440
Yeah.
We got work to do.

01:31:03.057 --> 01:31:04.929
- Yeah.
- Dr. Gold, it's about Badham again.

01:31:04.929 --> 01:31:07.781
- So she's gonna be all right?
- Okay. A broken nose. She'll be fine.

01:31:07.781 --> 01:31:09.091
Thank you very much.

01:31:12.982 --> 01:31:17.525
Miss Delano. Am I glad to see you.
I can't tell you

01:31:17.525 --> 01:31:20.379
what an experience this has been
for all of us down in Las Vegas.

01:31:20.379 --> 01:31:22.156
We were so relieved...

01:31:22.220 --> 01:31:24.836
when we learned that they had found
you and that you were all right.

01:31:24.836 --> 01:31:27.113
Listen,
I know that this has been...

01:31:28.391 --> 01:31:31.663
extremely traumatic for you,
but I'm here to assure you

01:31:31.663 --> 01:31:33.762
that every precaution
has been taken.

01:31:33.762 --> 01:31:37.203
- We're gonna get you home safe.
- I have to see my friends first.

01:31:37.446 --> 01:31:39.188
Oh, the O'Hara's.
Well, you know what?

01:31:39.749 --> 01:31:43.075
I think it would be safer if we just
went straight from here to the airport.

01:31:43.075 --> 01:31:45.649
They don't even know
what happened to me last night.

01:31:45.753 --> 01:31:47.522
Well, you could give 'em
a phone call.

01:31:47.522 --> 01:31:51.801
No, no, I'm sorry. If I decide
to go back and testify,

01:31:51.801 --> 01:31:54.269
I want to see my friends first.

01:31:56.793 --> 01:31:58.452
Well, I guess, uh,

01:31:59.020 --> 01:32:02.120
a quick side trip wouldn't do
too much harm.

01:32:02.358 --> 01:32:03.106
Not at all.

01:32:03.106 --> 01:32:04.942
And I'll stay with you
until you're on the plane.

01:32:04.942 --> 01:32:06.034
Thanks, Gina.

01:32:40.643 --> 01:32:43.443
- Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, shut up.
- Yeah, yeah, yeah.

01:32:45.418 --> 01:32:48.192
I'll let the dog out.
Will you grab my bag in there?

01:32:48.192 --> 01:32:49.172
Got it.

01:32:50.908 --> 01:32:51.793
Whoa!

01:32:52.161 --> 01:32:56.965
Archie! Archie! Archie!

01:32:59.003 --> 01:33:00.720
Archie, stop!

01:33:03.797 --> 01:33:06.540
- Archie, you come back here right now!
- Archie!

01:33:07.069 --> 01:33:09.217
- Archie! Archie!
- Stop it, Archie! Don't...

01:33:09.217 --> 01:33:13.799
- Come back here!
- Aw, sic 'em, Archie. Eat the cat.

01:33:14.531 --> 01:33:16.353
So I asked her to marry me.

01:33:16.496 --> 01:33:20.060
- Really? What'd she say?
- She hung up on me.

01:33:20.870 --> 01:33:23.935
- You asked her on the phone?
- Yeah, I asked her on the phone.

01:33:23.935 --> 01:33:27.642
Remember? I'm stuck on an island?
I'm at a dinner party, I can't get away.

01:33:28.493 --> 01:33:31.138
Dumb, stupid idea.
I know. Sorry.

01:33:31.138 --> 01:33:33.199
I'm sorry
I ruined my life.

01:33:33.736 --> 01:33:35.916
I'm sorry the suspect
got shot by my gun.

01:33:35.916 --> 01:33:37.878
I'm sorry the Mercedes
went into the bay.

01:33:37.878 --> 01:33:40.977
- What about me gettin' hit?
- Sorry about that too.

01:33:40.977 --> 01:33:44.267
- And me rollin' down the stairs?
- I'm sorry about that too.

01:33:44.267 --> 01:33:46.753
- And my moustache?
- All right!

01:33:47.027 --> 01:33:49.421
What are you gonna do,
blame the deficit on me?

01:33:56.473 --> 01:34:01.277
Just... really sorry
that she walked out on me.

01:34:05.963 --> 01:34:10.065
Dad... we still have
each other.

01:34:10.681 --> 01:34:12.516
A reason to live.

01:34:22.843 --> 01:34:25.823
- Chris?
- Hmm?

01:34:26.276 --> 01:34:27.568
They're back.

01:34:29.506 --> 01:34:32.731
- Who?
- Gina and the woman I love.

01:34:34.299 --> 01:34:37.383
- Cops.
- Who's the other one?

01:34:38.339 --> 01:34:39.541
- Lawyer.
- Lawyer.

01:34:39.541 --> 01:34:42.432
- They're going back to Vegas.
- I'm sure gonna miss 'er.

01:34:42.432 --> 01:34:46.581
- Come on, let's get the hell outta here.
- Another car.

01:34:50.169 --> 01:34:52.261
More cops,
it looks like.

01:34:55.574 --> 01:34:58.280
- In a Mustang?
- Maybe another lawyer.

01:35:03.757 --> 01:35:06.770
This guy's got a gun.
Not a lawyer.

01:35:13.948 --> 01:35:16.475
She had to constantly
smear cream on herself.

01:35:16.586 --> 01:35:18.974
I spent a week
at the Mirage. I loved it there.

01:35:19.957 --> 01:35:22.694
Come on right in. Relax a minute.
Take a look at this, will you?

01:35:42.267 --> 01:35:43.770
- Get down!
- Down!

01:35:43.770 --> 01:35:47.268
- Get down, there's a man!
- Behind the tree! He's got a gun! Get down!

01:35:47.922 --> 01:35:50.308
- Oh, my God. Oh, my God, it's them!
- What?

01:35:50.308 --> 01:35:52.140
- Get down!
- There's a man!

01:35:52.883 --> 01:35:53.930
- Get down!
- Get down!

01:35:53.930 --> 01:35:56.356
Brian, Brian, it's them! It's those guys
that tried to kill me!

01:35:56.462 --> 01:36:00.180
Everybody, get down! No, not there,
not there! Get up here!

01:36:00.180 --> 01:36:02.709
Do it fast!
Keep your heads down!

01:36:05.441 --> 01:36:07.281
Police! Freeze!

01:36:11.538 --> 01:36:14.551
The idiots are shooting at us.
Stop shooting at us, you idiots.

01:36:16.141 --> 01:36:20.243
They think we're the bad guys.
Show 'em your badge.

01:36:20.243 --> 01:36:22.959
- They're never gonna believe we're cops.
- Gina's there, she'll tell 'em.

01:36:22.959 --> 01:36:24.640
Go on! Hold it up!

01:36:25.464 --> 01:36:28.344
Wait a minute.
Why don't you show 'em yours?

01:36:28.390 --> 01:36:29.863
You think I'm crazy?

01:36:30.099 --> 01:36:31.731
All right, all right!

01:36:31.826 --> 01:36:35.113
- Do it together. One, two, three.
- ... two, three.

01:36:35.113 --> 01:36:36.909
Don't shoot! We're cops!

01:36:39.191 --> 01:36:40.279
Great idea.

01:36:41.341 --> 01:36:44.595
- Can we shoot back?
- What if we kill 'em?

01:36:44.755 --> 01:36:46.572
- What if they kill us?
- Good point.

01:36:46.756 --> 01:36:50.731
Okay. You go,
I'll cover you. Go!

01:36:51.742 --> 01:36:54.717
Wait a minute.
Why don't... you go, and I cover?

01:36:54.717 --> 01:36:57.173
Because I'm already doing
the covering thing! Go on, go on!

01:36:57.465 --> 01:36:59.345
But you're older.
You got less to live for.

01:37:00.065 --> 01:37:02.782
- Get outta here!
- Don't shoot anybody.

01:37:14.885 --> 01:37:16.930
- Who'd you see?
- The same men.

01:37:16.930 --> 01:37:18.247
- The ones from last night?
- Yes.

01:37:18.345 --> 01:37:18.889
Oh, my God!

01:37:18.889 --> 01:37:21.267
Stop shooting! Stop shooting,
they're police!

01:37:21.267 --> 01:37:21.840
What?

01:37:21.840 --> 01:37:24.536
They're cops. Det. Lecce
and Reimers out of Seattle.

01:37:24.522 --> 01:37:26.961
They're with me.
Part of the stakeout next door.

01:37:26.961 --> 01:37:31.087
Bullshit! If they're cops, what the
hell are they shootin' at us for?

01:37:31.087 --> 01:37:33.985
- Because you're shooting at them!
- Call for backup.

01:37:41.747 --> 01:37:44.340
Chris, Bill, stop!
I told them you're cops!

01:37:52.128 --> 01:37:53.528
Oh, shit.

01:37:53.816 --> 01:37:57.804
- Steve. Steve! Hang in there, buddy.
- I'm all right.

01:38:09.393 --> 01:38:12.754
- What the hell are you doing?
- Hang on, Steve.

01:38:35.484 --> 01:38:36.179
In the basement!

01:38:36.179 --> 01:38:38.459
No, no, no! I gotta get her
outta the house!

01:38:40.444 --> 01:38:41.145
Go!

01:38:41.614 --> 01:38:45.556
- Tommy.
- You?!

01:38:46.859 --> 01:38:50.147
Jesus Christ, am I glad to see you.
I've been goin' nuts here.

01:38:50.147 --> 01:38:52.680
- Where is she?
- She's back there. Upstairs.

01:38:53.241 --> 01:38:54.931
It's great
workin' with you, Tom.

01:39:10.292 --> 01:39:12.320
- Bastard.
- I'm a cop.

01:39:14.568 --> 01:39:16.784
Run to the water.
Stay by the shore.

01:39:16.784 --> 01:39:18.724
Don't stop for anything.

01:39:20.920 --> 01:39:23.352
- Go!
- I can't.

01:39:23.352 --> 01:39:26.151
Go!
Jump, goddamn it!

01:39:56.317 --> 01:39:58.226
Throw out your gun!

01:39:59.529 --> 01:40:02.330
Come out with your hands
above your head!

01:40:03.131 --> 01:40:05.413
This is the police.
You're completely surrounded!

01:40:05.413 --> 01:40:08.246
- You got ten seconds!
- No, you got ten seconds!

01:40:08.246 --> 01:40:11.083
You kill her, we kill you.
It's that simple.

01:40:11.083 --> 01:40:13.154
She's a friend of yours.
Wanna see her die?

01:40:13.154 --> 01:40:14.370
I'm sorry.

01:40:14.420 --> 01:40:15.784
I'm sorry!

01:40:16.538 --> 01:40:20.699
You see. She's sorry.
Now back off.

01:40:20.767 --> 01:40:23.094
Back the hell off!
Now!

01:40:25.671 --> 01:40:28.049
Ooh, I don't like
what you're thinkin', ace.

01:40:28.846 --> 01:40:32.353
Cool heads, boys.
Cool heads.

01:40:50.413 --> 01:40:51.829
- Let's talk, gentlemen.
- No talk.

01:40:52.007 --> 01:40:53.695
Let's trade here.
What do you care?

01:40:54.641 --> 01:40:57.211
You want 'er alive, right? I don't
care about 'er, you can have 'er.

01:40:57.325 --> 01:40:59.226
But I get the other one.
I get who I came for.

01:40:59.226 --> 01:41:01.210
She walks away and I walk away.
Works for me.

01:41:01.210 --> 01:41:03.293
Shoot her. I don't care.
You're not walkin' outta here.

01:41:03.293 --> 01:41:05.057
Listen, nobody's gonna
blame you guys.

